{"tid":1788872,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLIND真係好愛BLACKPINK","createTime":"2019-12-19T04:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T09:27:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6032924efb669c28dec0192fec0526ecd057b2f5","tid":1788872,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1576730537.A.8FE.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FKoreaStar%2FM.1576730537.A.8FE.html&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6mjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=a578adf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1576730537.A.8FE.html</a><br />\nBLACKPINK的國外粉絲把他們的抗議規模擴大了。<br />\n<br />\n原文只抓了3張圖，<br />\n我把組織這次抗議的美國粉絲推特站上有貼的地點都放上來。<br />\nGyeonggi Building<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8OWL7g6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8OWL7g6.jpg&h=fd4be6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSeoul Station<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vjtzkGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvjtzkGW.jpg&h=4bd07069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMyeongdong Red Eye<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9qjOBMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9qjOBMK.jpg&h=be55754b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKTX MEDIA WALL<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HfcSxsU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHfcSxsU.jpg&h=c917c1cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHongik University Station-1<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/so2e7eF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fso2e7eF.png&h=f2af7a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHongik University Station-2<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/58sJcjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F58sJcjE.jpg&h=1ddb91bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGongdeok Station-1<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K8O1Mgz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK8O1Mgz.png&h=71a444b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDMC Station<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E1dc32s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FE1dc32s.jpg&h=c64ca2ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIncheon Airport<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S8FI7vB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FS8FI7vB.jpg&h=8c62ec78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留言：<br />\n<br />\n1. 她們巡演的場次好多。這似乎已成YG藝人的習慣了，1年1張專輯，然後都在巡演。YG只專注在巡演賺錢上。<br />\n<br />\n2. YG就是藥局所以我懂，顆顆顆。<br />\n<br />\n3. Teddy不再為她們寫歌了嗎？請以除了Teddy之外的製作人寫的歌回歸吧！<br />\n<br />\n4. BLACKPINK看起來就像沒什麼行程的新人團體。<br />\n<br />\n5. BLACKPINK的外國粉絲真是驚人... 飯上YG的團對他們來說太慘了。<br />\n<br />\n6. 我想看BLACKPINK的年末舞台... 我相信如果她們參加年末節目，一定會是熱門話題。<br />\n<br />\n7. 但BLACKPINK人氣已經很高了，即使1年只回歸1次。<br />\n<br />\n8. 呃... 這段日子裡除了成員們發的IG外，我根本看不到BLACKPINK。<br />\n<br />\n9. 所有YG藝人的回歸間隔都愈來愈長...<br />\n<br />\n10. 對「藥局」講再多也沒用。"},{"pid":"41751f22c784197c45d74fe60b636a226489e9de","tid":1788872,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"bp<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81da49ee5aa63936a53de5395d1ba52bab8fc1ce","tid":1788872,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"藥局<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d8fcb40ec37b67cc24892a504bcff0425bf1a4","tid":1788872,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"blind<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba30635f83c64981b8502081ad6efbd59535060","tid":1788872,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"我係blind啊屌"},{"pid":"998f0fa00459adc55f506b223366a779a567255b","tid":178